    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Head of male specimen of Rhodostrophia calabra (PETAGNA, 1787). 2a, lateral view of the head, notice the eyes, labial palp and quadripectinate antennae; 2b, ventral view of the antenna; 2c, lateral view of the antenna, antennal flagellum ventrally dentate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6378572/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6378568>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Wing venation of Rhodostrophia calabra (PETAGNA, 1787), type species of the genus." ;
